{
  "text": "Now, the obvious only significant difference, I believe, between the positive and negative adept in using this shuttle is the way they had polarized. Is there a relationship between the archetypes of the spirit and whether the polarization is either positive or negative? Is, for instance, the positive calling through the sixteenth and the negative calling through the fifteenth archetype? I am very confused on these points and I imagine that question is poor or meaningless. Can you answer that? I am Ra. It is a challenge to answer such a query, for there is some confusion in its construction. However, we shall attempt to speak upon the subject. The adept, whether positive or negative, has the same Matrix. The Potentiator is also identical. Due to the Catalyst of each adept the adept may begin to pick and choose that into which it shall look further. The Experience of the Spirit, that which you have called the Moon, is then, by far, the more manifest of influences upon the polarity of the adept. Even the most unhappy of experiences, shall we say, which seem to occur in the Catalyst of the adept, seen from the viewpoint of the spirit, may, with the discrimination possible in shadow, be worked with until light equaling the light of brightest noon descends upon the adept and positive or service-to-others illumination has occurred. The service-to-self adept will satisfy itself with the shadows and, grasping the light of day, will toss back the head in grim laughter, preferring the darkness.",
  "timestamps": {
    "segment": [
      {
        "segment": "Now, the obvious only significant difference, I believe, between the positive and negative adept in using this shuttle is the way they had polarized.",
        "start_offset": 0,
        "end_offset": 149,
        "start": 2.26,
        "end": 37.621
      },
      {
        "segment": "Is there a relationship between the archetypes of the spirit and whether the polarization is either positive or negative?",
        "start_offset": 150,
        "end_offset": 271,
        "start": 37.661,
        "end": 58.861
      },
      {
        "segment": "Is, for instance, the positive calling through the sixteenth and the negative calling through the fifteenth archetype?",
        "start_offset": 272,
        "end_offset": 390,
        "start": 63.461,
        "end": 75.321
      },
      {
        "segment": "I am very confused on these points and I imagine that question is poor or meaningless.",
        "start_offset": 391,
        "end_offset": 477,
        "start": 75.441,
        "end": 80.761
      },
      {
        "segment": "Can you answer that?",
        "start_offset": 478,
        "end_offset": 498,
        "start": 81.281,
        "end": 84.662
      },
      {
        "segment": "I am Ra.",
        "start_offset": 499,
        "end_offset": 507,
        "start": 84.882,
        "end": 86.882
      },
      {
        "segment": "It is a challenge to answer such a query, for there is some confusion in its construction.",
        "start_offset": 508,
        "end_offset": 598,
        "start": 86.982,
        "end": 118.562
      },
      {
        "segment": "However, we shall attempt to speak upon the subject.",
        "start_offset": 599,
        "end_offset": 651,
        "start": 120.382,
        "end": 130.862
      },
      {
        "segment": "The adept, whether positive or negative, has the same Matrix.",
        "start_offset": 652,
        "end_offset": 713,
        "start": 135.902,
        "end": 153.323
      },
      {
        "segment": "The Potentiator is also identical.",
        "start_offset": 714,
        "end_offset": 748,
        "start": 157.763,
        "end": 167.763
      },
      {
        "segment": "Due to the Catalyst of each adept the adept may begin to pick and choose that into which it shall look further.",
        "start_offset": 749,
        "end_offset": 860,
        "start": 172.463,
        "end": 205.504
      },
      {
        "segment": "The Experience of the Spirit, that which you have called the Moon, is then, by far, the more manifest of influences upon the polarity of the adept.",
        "start_offset": 861,
        "end_offset": 1008,
        "start": 209.324,
        "end": 250.924
      },
      {
        "segment": "Even the most unhappy of experiences, shall we say, which seem to occur in the Catalyst of the adept, seen from the viewpoint of the spirit, may, with the discrimination possible in shadow, be worked with until light equaling the light of brightest noon descends upon the adept and positive or service-to-others illumination has occurred.",
        "start_offset": 1009,
        "end_offset": 1347,
        "start": 250.944,
        "end": 341.146
      },
      {
        "segment": "The service-to-self adept will satisfy itself with the shadows and, grasping the light of day, will toss back the head in grim laughter, preferring the darkness.",
        "start_offset": 1348,
        "end_offset": 1509,
        "start": 344.726,
        "end": 382.107
      }
